prodNameC: 宙斯甲狀腺球蛋白IgG酵素連結免疫吸收分析檢測系統
prodNameE: Zeus Thyroglobulin IgG ELISA test system
ingredientsDesc:
1.Plate:  96 wells configured in twelve 1x8-well strips coated with purified human thyroglobulin antigen (> 96%).
2.Conjugate:  Conjugated (horseradish peroxidase) goat anti-human IgG (r chain specific). 
3.Positive Control (Human Serum): One, 0.35 mL vial.
4.Calibrator A (Human Serum): One, 0.35 mL vial.
5.Calibrator B (Human Serum): One, 0.35 mL vial.
6.Calibrator C (Human Serum): One, 0.35mL vial.
7.Calibrator D (Human Serum): One, 0.35mL vial.
8.Negative Control (Human Serum): One, 0.35 mL vial.
9.Sample diluent: One 30 mL bottle containing Tween-20, bovine serum albumin and phosphate-buffered-saline, (pH 7.2 ± 0.2).
10.TMB: One 15 mL amber bottle containing 3,3’,5,5’-tetramethylbenzidine (TMB). 
11.Stop solution: One 15 mL bottle containing 1M H2SO4, 0.7M HCl. 
12.Wash buffer concentrate (10X): One 100 mL bottle containing a 10X concentrated phosphate-buffered-saline and Tween-20 solution.
applicantAddr: 台北市信義區松德路７４號８樓
efficacy: 定性及半定量人類血清中的甲狀腺球蛋白(thyroglobulin)對應之IgG抗體。
